title: Ending Soon: This Month’s GTA+ Benefits
headline: Ending Soon: This Month’s GTA+ Benefits
content:
Thank you for being a GTA+ Member. Don’t forget to claim all of your GTA+ benefits by October 8:

— The Canis Terminus Patrol (Emergency)
— 50% off Bail Offices and their Upgrades and Modifications
— Double Rewards on Dispatch Work
— The Stun Gun at the Gun Van
— Double Rewards on Bounty Targets
— And more

Membership renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
